	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "The reading of Fast. Cap. as revised by Degrassi from fresh scrutiny of the stone removes the basis for modelling this name on that of P. Cornelius Scapula, the Consul of 328." .
